-to-ps4-and-xbox-one-after-all-064100551.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1927ed5f-91ba-459f-b84e-58b55b159491</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 02 Aug 2023 06:41:00 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690954239</ingested><modified> 2023-08-02T05:30:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="630" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/02d05290-30f2-11ee-af7f-6a52060cfc2c" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="630" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/02d05290-30f2-11ee-af7f-6a52060cfc2c" width="1200"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA['Star Wars: Jedi Survivor' will be ported to PS4 and Xbox One after all]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA['Star Wars: Jedi Survivor' will be ported to PS4 and Xbox One after all]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[TweetDeck's new name is 'XPro']]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-launches-new-tweetdeck-as-the-old-version-breaks-down-231939160.html">TweetDeck</a>已经<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://9to5google.com/2023/08/01/tweetdeck-xpro/">开始显示出它无法毫发无伤地逃脱 Twitter 大规模品牌重塑的迹象</a>。如果您在注销时查看该工具的登录页面，您会在网站的左上角看到“XPro”，表明其新名称。不过，目前差不多就是这样了——该页面仍然显示标志性的 Twitter 小鸟标志，并且仍然称 TweetDeck 是“为 Twitter 上的人们提供的强大的实时工具”。是的，它的 URL 仍然位于 Twitter.com 域中。</p><p> Twitter 在 7 月份一夜之间<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-is-rebranding-twitter-to-x-and-killing-the-bird-logo-165944573.html">更名为“X”</a> ，这让我们震惊不已，埃隆·马斯克在推文中宣布了这一变化，据报道，随后又向他的员工发送了有关此事的电子邮件。此后，该社交网络开始实施变革，将推特小鸟换成看起来很普通的“X”徽标，该徽标显然会“<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1683947705876328450">随着时间的推移而演变”，</a>并将推文重命名为“帖子”，将转发重命名为“转发”。 7 月底，谷歌和苹果都分别在 Play 商店和 App Store 上将社交网络应用程序重新列为“X”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这一举动虽然很突然，但对于那些多年来关注马斯克职业生涯的人来说，也许并不感到意外。马斯克以偏爱“X”品牌而闻名，在被免去首席执行官职务之前，他<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/history/2023/07/25/elon-musk-paypal-twitter-x-rebrand/">曾想将 PayPal 更名</a>为 X.com。这位高管还将 Twitter 的母公司更名为 X Corp。他表示，该社交网络的新名称将帮助其拓展业务，成为具有<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-ceo-teases-banking-and-payment-plans-in-memo-about-x-rebrand-175218664.html">支付和银行功能</a>的“一切应用程序”。但批评者对品牌重塑的成功表示怀疑，一些<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90927580/elon-musk-twitter-rebrand-x-bad-idea">人称其为</a>“自接管以来（马斯克）所做的最愚蠢的事情”，并且现在使公司变得<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/marcuscollins/2023/07/30/the-real-lesson-to-be-learned-from-twitters-rebrand/?sh=14480ee41fd2">更加不那么可识别</a>， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:time;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=7212db91-cd64-4c1b-ab0d-1d1c998f089e&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=time&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI3MjEyZGI5MS1jZDY0LTRjMWItYWIwZC0xZDFjOTk4ZjA4OWUiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly90aW1lLmNvbS82Mjk3MzAzL3R3aXR0ZXIteC1yZWJyYW5kLWNvc3QvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxYmI0YWQ3OS1mZWVjLTRjYjktOWMzYi1jMGE2ODNkMjBiNWYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAeowi3e0WO_nPI2h5ZbvO-0WSm95P5ADYk1ct_7CjGd7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6297303%2Ftwitter-x-rebrand-cost%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">价值</a>也更低。</p><p>尽管受到批评，推特品牌的抹除工作目前仍在顺利进行。 TweetDeck 不会长期保留 TweetDeck，并且在不久的将来也不会免费使用。该公司此前曾指出，它将被锁定在付费墙后面，并且<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-launches-new-tweetdeck-as-the-old-version-breaks-down-231939160.html">仅供 Blue 订阅者使用</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tweetdecks-new-name-is-xpro-052613174.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tweetdecks-new-name-is-xpro-052613174.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1bb4ad79-feec-4cb9-9c3b-c0a683d20b5f</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 02 Aug 2023 05:26:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690959993</ingested><modified> 2023-08-02T07:06:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1013" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d0dd6420-30e8-11ee-bef0-78363bdb608d" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1013" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d0dd6420-30e8-11ee-bef0-78363bdb