rder:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>随着转向移动设备，游戏并没有发生显着变化。然而，开发人员认为<em>Unpacking</em>对于触摸来说是“完美的”，因为你可以用手指拖动对象并通过触觉反馈感知世界。不管这是否属实，便携性可能很有吸引力。当您刚搬到一个新地方时，这可能是最适合玩的游戏 - 您可以在常用的游戏硬件还没有收拾好时就启动它。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/zen-moving-game-unpacking-comes-to-android-and-ios-on-august-24th-214513079.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/zen-moving-game-unpacking-comes-to-android-and-ios-on-august-24th-214513079.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8f66a209-7f9e-42fa-962a-768a1d5d0f36</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:45:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690924640</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T21:17:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a747b760-30ab-11ee-b23f-e439d370288a" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a747b760-30ab-11ee-b23f-e439d370288a" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Humble Games