arts-for-xbox-gamepads-174023573.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9614cf41-5f9a-4fd4-8426-11b623678e2a</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 17:40:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690911625</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T17:40:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="3049" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4b636b00-308e-11ee-9cbd-df316645a4a9" width="4573"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3049" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4b636b00-308e-11ee-9cbd-df316645a4a9" width="4573"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[picture alliance via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[04 November 2021, Berlin: A controller of the Xbox Series X game console is on the table. Playstation 5 and Xbox Series X have been on the market for a year, but there are still supply problems. Photo: Fabian Sommer/dpa (Photo by Fabian Sommer/picture alliance via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Xbox Series X]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Amazon's virtual healthcare service is now available in every state]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>亚马逊的数字医疗保健方法现已在全国范围内推广。该公司已将 Clinic <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.aboutamazon.com/news/retail/amazon-clinic-available-nationwide">扩展</a>到全美 50 个州以及华盛顿特区。除了 34 个州的纯文本对话之外，您还可以在全国范围内进行临床医生视频访问。这两种途径都可以通过亚马逊网站和移动应用程序获得。</p><p> Clinic 于 11 月推出，旨在为 30 多种常见健康问题提供治疗，例如避孕处方、偏头痛和红眼病。您选择远程医疗服务提供者，填写表格并与临床医生取得联系。您不需要预约或保险，而且在您联系之前费用就可见。亚马逊希望您通过其<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-pharmacy-134356646.html">内部药房</a>服务配药任何必要的处方，但任何第三方药房都是一种选择。该公司补充说，“未来几个月”将提供更多条件的帮助。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Clinic 是亚马逊长期努力的一部分，旨在涵盖医疗保健的许多方面。它于 2018 年<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-28-amazon-buys-pillpack-healthcare-online-pharmacy.html">收购了 PillPack</a> （Pharmacy 的基础），并在 2019 年至 2022 年间向自己的员工以及其他公司提供 Care 远程医疗服务。亚马逊最近完成了以 39 亿美元<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-completes-one-medical-acquisition-163431975.html">收购 One Medical 的交易</a>，将其转变为一家拥有实体店、虚拟选项和实验室测试的初级医疗保健提供商。在适当的情况下，您可能只需要与亚马逊企业进行互动。</p><p>这些举措引起了监管机构的审查。尽管联邦贸易委员会在 2 月份表示不会对 One Medical 的收购提出质疑，但它警告称，仍在调查此次合并是否可能因获取健康数据而产生反竞争和隐私问题。欧盟委员会表示，如果发现问题，可能会在稍后对该交易提出质疑。不过，就目前而言，亚马逊的医疗保健雄心并未面临重大阻力——它现在已成为传统诊所的替代方案，至少对于日常问题而言是如此。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/amazons-virtual-healthcare-service-is-now-available-in-every-state-171827351.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazons-virtual-healthcare-service-is-now-available-in-every-state-171827351.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cc34f829-9f25-4299-8bec-6fda52386971</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 17:18:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690909774</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T17:09:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f734e800-3084-11ee-9ff7-c2fcdfb18cc4" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f734e800-3084-11ee-9ff7-c2fcdfb18cc4" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Amazon]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Amazon Clinic]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Clinic]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>